data.description: Welcome to your future home! From the moment you walk in, you'll discover an open layout that seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen with its breakfast bar making for easy entertaining. Retreat to the expansive primary bedroom with its ensuite bathroom. Recent updates include gleaming refinished hardwood floors throughout the main level and a stylishly renovated hallway bathroom. The ground floor offers endless possibilities with a versatile den/playroom, an additional bedroom or office, and a recreational room that opens up to a sprawling deck and fenced-in rear yard, perfect for outdoor enjoyment. Located conveniently close to NYC transportation, as well as an array of restaurants, schools, and parks, this home offers the perfect balance of comfort and convenience. Experience the best of suburban living in this delightful retreat!
